Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to wear nice clothes and be more beautiful than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, that person will turn around and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll turn around because I'm pretty.
