Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mayumi! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My papa just came back and brought lots of western clothes with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice having a father like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought accessories with him too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing special really, when he \Ncomes back he never stops talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,, I guess you're right, I should be happy that he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He got back in time for my birthday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're coming to my party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N - Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming too, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I... of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there boys coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are, Doi already said he is coming but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayumi! Are you going out with Doi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're going out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We just talk at school all the time and he's helped me a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've cleaned the blackboard for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He has such a kind voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After that I became curious about Doi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I looked at him,\Nhe was already looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, we don't even know who it's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have been delivered to the wrong house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all, that one piece makes me uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like it was made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mama, is it okay for me to wear that to Mayumi's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Do you want them all to laugh at me for wearing my own weird clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already got lots of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You just bought some more the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! Please, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just going to your friends house, why do you need to get all dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're going to the party today too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief! I was invited too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be the first time I see you in your own clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been nice if I could go wearing that one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Mama said she closed it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mama's fault... all her fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuko sure is late, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She even said she was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doi, let's go and play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my birthday today, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay. We'll bring Hashimoto too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I have to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi... look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was discharged a few days later and\N found out that Doi had transferred schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After talking to otther boys,\N they told me that he like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't worn that dress, \Nthat wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I still can't get rid of the regret I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After yesterday's dance, the one piece that\N should have disappeared was back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't checked properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too scared to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm still scared of that eerie\N one piece, everyday is filled with fear.
